<paragraph id="DD6800329A35AA7142D512F427349ED5" pageId="7" pageNumber="110">
INDIA. Sikkim, South District, Maenam WLS (Maenum 3), 2136 m alt., 
<geoCoordinate id="4F1EDEA5A3F23647B0D7C41B0FA5F8E4" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="1" value="27.25964">N27°15'34.7&quot;</geoCoordinate>
